price of three rubles puts an englishlanguage emblem saying 
manufactured exclusively for smash on them and sells them for 
35 rubles 
the seller who had a halfdozen shirts hanging from a line was 
asked how many such shirts he could sell in a weekend he refused 
to answer and said the query was a provocative question 
valery a muscovite with several days growth of beard and a 
widebrim black hat said he can buy the labeling and everything he 
needs for the sfinks denim line from associates at the market 
he also had for sale two childrens sweatsuits one with walt 
disneys bambi emblazoned on it for 20 rubles about 32 
he said he sells in moscow occasionally but prefers the soviet 
far east or siberia its too crowded here people have more 
money there because they earn higher salaries he said 
