<TEXT>
arab americans are parlaying the palestinian 
revolt against israeli occupation of the west bank and gaza strip 
into a surge of charitable contributions and domestic political 
gains 
last month the united palestine appeal and other charitable 
organizations raised 300000 to help palestinians continue a 
threemonth resistance campaign that has captured the worlds 
attention according to david sadd executive director of the 
national association of arab americans 
this compares with some 1 million these groups raised in all of 
1987 and does not include the checks sent by american palestinians 
to their relatives in the occupied territories said sadd whose 
group is a major lobbyist for an estimated 23 million arab 
americans 
theres real pride about the courageous palestinians we want 
