florida supreme court ruling that the public has no right to hear 
or see pretrial statements called depositions given during 
criminal prosecutions 
in the case acted on today the florida court extended its 
ruling on pretrial materials in criminal cases to depositions and 
other pretrial materials in civil cases 
hawkins who lost her senate seat in the 1986 election to 
democrat bob graham a former florida governor injured her back in 
