violates the 1947 un headquarters treaty by which the united 
states agreed to allow all un missions to operate 
the plo was granted observer status by the 159member world 
body which considers the organization the only legitimate 
representative of the palestinian people the plo participates in 
un debates on the middle east but does not have the right to vote 
