to education health care and local governments according to the 
bill roemer has voiced opposition to a lottery 
also referred to a senate committee were bills to transfer the 
functions of some agencies to other departments reduce the 
interest rate on some refunds and payments being delayed by the 
governor in order to save cash and abolish most special funds in 
the state treasury 
