at some sites we could have used 20 people for a year instead 
of three for two months vallin said 
relations with the tunnel builders have been fairly good even 
if they sometimes push a little hard the archaeologists and the 
construction men meet once a week to discuss schedules 
the vast range of history covered by the digs requires a wide 
