european central bank during their landmark meeting but agreed to 
meet again before the summer in paris 
gerhard stoltenberg the west german finance minister said 
mondays meeting reviewed economic developments in the two nations 
analyzed budget and tax plans and began examining ways of boosting 
cooperation in monetary policy 
french finance minister edouard balladur also praised the 
