pretty much a nonevent 
bank of new york began its hostile attempt to acquire irving 
last september a struggle that has been widely followed by bankers 
because unfriendly takeovers are unusual in the banking industry 
its tender offer expires at midnight on april 15 
irvings board last week amended its antitakeover plan to make 
it harder for a slate of new irving directors to scuttle rights if 
they win a proxy fight at irvings annual meeting april 21 
bank of new york already has nominated a 16director slate to 
compete with irvings slate at the meeting the bank said it would 
fight irvings amended antitakeover plan in the courts 
