denverbased concern that provides investment advice and had about 
915 million in funds under management at the end of february 
according to kansas city southerns vice president and secretary 
albert mauro 
for the fiscal year ended dec 31 kansas city southern reported 
a profit of 177 million or 182 a share on revenue of 5076 
million 
