trw inc said monday it has reached an 
agreement to buy chilton corp from borgwarner corp for about 
360 million 
chilton operates consumer credit reporting accounts receivable 
management and related businesses chilton headquartered in 
dallas is a wholly owned subsidiary of borgwarner based in 
chicago 
chilton will become a part of trw information systems group 
which provides information and information processing services to 
the financial services industry trw information systems is located 
in long beach calif 
chilton has an excellent reputation combining its resources 
with those of trw will provide consumers and the consumer 
information market with better and more efficient service said 
richard dc whilden trw executive vice president and general 
manager of trw information systems group 
chilton president van smith said the combination enhances the 
companies ability to provide new products and services 
borgwarners products and services include automotive 
components chemicals and plastics and protective services the 
clevelandbased trw provides high technology products and services 
for the space and defense automotive and information systems 
markets 
